sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant IN as Intake λ
    participant SNS as SNS topic
    participant EQ as enrich-q<br/>(SQS — the ONLY stage=enrich subscriber)
    participant EN as Enricher λ<br/>(reserved concurrency 5–20)
    participant CACHE as Signature Cache<br/>(DDB hash→enrichedText)
    participant BUD as TenantAiBudget<br/>(atomic counter)
    participant CTX as Context Store<br/>(payload + allow-listed views)
    participant MASK as PII Masker
    participant LLM as Bedrock<br/>(Haiku, temp 0, no retention)
    participant VAL as Validator<br/>(schema + groundedness)
    participant DLQ as enrich-DLQ<br/>(alarm at depth ≥ 1)
    participant CH as channel queues<br/>(inbox·email·slack)

    IN->>SNS: publish (type.aiEnrichment=true)<br/>attrs: stage=enrich
    SNS->>EQ: only enrich-q matches stage=enrich
    Note over EQ,CH: THE MESSAGE WAITS HERE —<br/>no channel queue can see it until stage=deliver

    EN->>EQ: receive (concurrency-capped)
    EN->>CACHE: GET hash(typeId + key-fields bucketed)
    alt cache hit
        CACHE-->>EN: enrichedText — zero model cost
    else cache miss
        EN->>BUD: atomic check monthlyTokens < cap
        alt budget_denied
            BUD-->>EN: denied
            Note over EN: NO retry — admin alert.<br/>Parks until budget/config changes
        else ok
            EN->>CTX: fetch payloadRef + allow-listed views<br/>(≤2 fetches ≤150ms, circuit-broken)
            CTX-->>EN: payload + context
            EN->>MASK: allow-list → PII→placeholders
            MASK-->>EN: masked prompt fields
            Note over EN: token bucket matched to Bedrock RPM/TPM quota<br/>circuit breaker if error rate sustained
            EN->>LLM: invoke (5s timeout, temp 0)
            alt throttled (429) / timeout / 5xx
                LLM-->>EN: fail
                Note over EN,EQ: classify → backoff retry via SQS visibility<br/>~30s → 2m → 8m (jitter) — 429 burns no budget
                EN-->>EQ: message stays queued (attempt++)
            else response
                LLM-->>EN: JSON output
                EN->>VAL: schema + groundedness<br/>(every value ∈ payload∪context)
                alt invalid
                    VAL-->>EN: rejected — one retry, then DLQ
                else valid
                    VAL-->>EN: ok
                    EN->>CACHE: SET hash → enrichedText (TTL=type TTL)
                    EN->>BUD: ADD tokensUsed (billing)
                end
            end
        end
    end

    alt enrichment succeeded (cache hit or validated)
        EN->>SNS: REPUBLISH — attrs: stage=deliver + enriched fields
        SNS->>CH: channel queues now see it (filter: stage=deliver)
        Note over CH: channel λs render the ENRICHED content —<br/>one version, identical on every channel (p99 ≤ 10s AI SLO)
    else maxReceiveCount (5) exhausted
        EQ->>DLQ: move message
        Note over DLQ: ALARM fires (mandatory) — audit: enrich_dlq{reason}<br/>operator fixes cause → one-click redrive (idempotent) → delivers
    end
